Hyperborean gnomes are a race of small humanoids that inhabit the more
habitable rural areas of Hyperborea. They are bright and nimble, with a
natural resistance to variations in the environment. They have a slight
tendency to work towards the causes of good, if only because they are
subject to attack by the forces of evil. Like all gnomes, they are quite
small compared to other races, and have difficulty managing larger weapons.
